  "title": "Fantasy 3D Weapons CIT",
  "description": "Adds 3D weapon models to MC! (Custom Item Textures)",
  "body": "Hello! I always loved fantasy weapon designs, so I wanted to bring some of those ideas into Minecraft. You can apply these models to any axe or sword by renaming it with an anvil.\n\n![Website](https://i.imgur.com/GGNWmau.gif)\n<br><br>\n<a href=\"https://mc3dweapons.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/INeH1HZ.png\" /></a>\n<br>\n\n<br>\n<h3>The list below is incomplete. Refer to the website for all weapons!</h3>\n<a href=\"https://mc3dweapons.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://mc3dweapons.com/</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/9YuWUr8guC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tZDyXb1/discord-button-3-DWP.png\" /></a>\n<br><br>\n<h3>Join my discord server for info, updates, behind the scenes, and more!</h3>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/9YuWUr8guC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://discord.gg/9YuWUr8guC</a>\n<br><br><br>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/36syldk.jpeg\"/></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/n1SJr86.jpeg\"/></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d5dCp7G.jpeg\" /></p>\n<br>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/k2nG1b/2017_12_27_16_29_27.png\" /></p>\n\n<br>\n<h3>If you are playing on a version lower than 1.21.5:</h3> \n<h4>The pack requires OptiFine, which can be downloaded here:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://optifine.net/home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://optifine.net/home</a>\n\n<br>\n<h4>If you're playing on Fabric, this pack requires CIT Resewn:</h3>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cit-resewn\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cit-resewn</a>\n\n<br>\n<h4>You will need to download the OptiFine-compatible version of the pack.</h3>",
